Wannan babban mataki ne na musamman ga masana'antar kwalliyar da ke da daraja na Burtaniya, wanda ke ci gaba da bunkasa duk da raguwar tallace-tallace na kayan ado da kayan gida. Ana gwada manyan sassan kwalliyar a shagunan 11 a fadin ƙasar, kuma idan sun yi nasara za a faɗaɗa su zuwa wasu shagunan a shekara mai zuwa.
Ana saka hannun jari a cikin kayayyakin ado domin manyan kantuna suna neman su cika ɗakunan ajiya da aka riga aka ajiye don talabijin, microwaves da kayan gida.
Sainsbury's ta ce za ta ninka yawan kayayyakin da take samarwa don yin ado da su zuwa 3,000, wanda a karon farko ya ƙunshi wasu nau'ikan kayayyaki kamar Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman da kuma Dr. PawPaw.
Hakanan, ana ba da ƙarin sarari ga alamun da suke wanzu kamar L'Oreal, Maybelline da Burt's Bees, kuma suna samun yankunan kansu na musamman kamar shagunan Boots.
A nan gaba, yawancin kayayyakin da ke cikin kantin sayar da kayayyaki za su zama masu cin ganyayyaki, domin matasa suna bukatar su yi hakan.
Bugu da ƙari, kamfanin sayar da kayan yaji na The Fragrance Shop yana gwada shagunan haya a shagunan Sainsbury's guda biyu, wanda aka buɗe a makon da ya gabata a Croydon, kudancin London, kuma za a buɗe wani a Selly Oak, Birmingham, a ƙarshen wannan shekara.
