Peter Jones yana fushi bayan da Holly Willoughby ta janye daga kwangilar fam miliyan 11
Peter Jones, dan wasan kwaikwayo na Dragons Den ya bar gidansa yana cikin fushi lokacin da mai gabatar da shirye-shiryen talabijin Holly Willoughby ya janye daga kwangilar fam miliyan 11 da ya yi da alamar salon rayuwarsa don mayar da hankali kan sabbin kwangilarsa da Marks da Spencer da kuma ITV
Willoughby ba shi da lokaci don alamar abinci da gidajensu ga Truly.
An kwatanta kamfanonin su da Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop.
Wani mai shekaru 37 da haihuwa da ke shirya shirin "This Morning" ya sanar da cewa zai bar gidansa a shafinsa na Instagram.
Holly Willoughby ta fusata Peter Jones na Dragons Den ta hanyar janyewa daga kasuwancin rayuwarsu mai fa'ida a cikin 'yan kwanakin nan, kuma yanzu tana shirin mayar da hankali kan sabbin yarjejeniyoyin da ta yi da Marks & Spencer da kuma ITV.
Wata majiya ta ce, a ranar Talata, a wani taro mai tsanani da aka yi a hedkwatar kasuwancin Jones a Marlowe, Buckinhamshire, 'yar talabijin ta ce sabon kwangilar ta da ta kai fam miliyan 1.5 ba za ta ba Truly isasshen lokaci ba don yin amfani da kayan abinci da kuma wurin zama.
An kwatanta wannan kamfani da Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop brand kuma an zarge shi da ninka dukiyar Willoughby da ake kiyasta a matsayin £11m.
Bayan da Willoughby mai shekara 37 ya sanar a shafinsa na Instagram cewa zai bar Truly, Jones ya tashi daga Birtaniya zuwa wani daga cikin gidajen hutu.
Wata majiya ta ce, "True" shi ne ainihin aikin da Holly ya yi.
Wannan shi ne shirinsa na dogon lokaci da ya sa ya tabbata cewa zai ci gaba da rayuwa na shekaru biyu masu zuwa.
Da ya yanke shawarar fita daga gidansa, ya ba da mamaki ga kowa.
Babu wanda zai yi imani da abin da ya faru a ranar Talata da ke kusa da fitowar.
A hedkwatar Marlow, akwai wani shago mai cike da kayayyakin da suke jiran sayarwa.
Wani mai shirya wannan taron yana ɗaya daga cikin manyan taurari masu cin riba a ƙasar Burtaniya, kuma masana sun ce barinsa zai iya jawo asarar miliyoyin kuɗi ga kamfanin don saka hannun jari a cikin kayayyaki, daga matashin wuta zuwa kyandirori da tufafi zuwa kayan abinci na gida, har ma da jinkirin wallafawa.
Hakan zai iya nufin cewa mun daina abokantaka na dogon lokaci.
