'Yan Macedonia a cikin kuri'ar raba gardama game da canja sunan ƙasar
A ranar Lahadi, 'yan Macedonia sun amince da sauya sunan ƙasar zuwa Jamhuriyar Macedonia ta Arewa, wanda zai magance hamayya da ta yi shekaru da yawa da ke hana ƙasar shiga cikin Tarayyar Turai da NATO.
Girka, wadda ke da yankin Macedonia, ta ce sunan makwabciyarta ta arewa a zahiri tana da'awar yankin da take ciki, saboda haka ta yi hamayya da samun damar shiga EU da NATO.
Gwamnatocin kasashen sun rattaba hannu a kan sabon yarjejeniyar a watan Yuni, amma masu adawa da kishin kasa sun ce sauyin zai raunana asalin kabilar Slavic mafiya rinjaye a Macedonia.
Shugaban kasa Gjorge Ivanov ya sanar da cewa ba zai yi zabe ba, kuma yakin neman zabe na neman kada kuri'un ya haifar da shakku kan ko za a iya samun kashi 50 cikin dari da ake bukata domin samun sakamako mai kyau.
Tambayar da aka yi a kan takardar zabe ita ce: 'Shin kuna goyon bayan NATO da EU na amincewa da yarjejeniyar da aka yi da Girka?
Masu goyon bayan sauya sunayen, kamar Firayim Minista Zoran Zaev, sun yi zaton cewa ya cancanci a biya wannan farashin domin Macedonia, wadda ta tashi daga faɗuwar Yugoslavia, ta iya neman shiga cikin EU da NATO.
'Yau na zo ne don in yi zabe a madadin makomar ƙasarmu, don matasan Makidoniya su rayu cikin 'yanci a matsayin' yan Tarayyar Turai, domin hakan na nufin rayuwa mafi aminci a gare mu duka,' in ji Olivera Georgijevska Skopje, mai shekara 79.
Ko da yake wannan zaɓe ba shi da tilas a doka, yawancin 'yan majalisa sun ce sun daraja sakamakon don ya yi tasiri.
Za a bukaci a yi rinjaye da kashi biyu bisa uku a majalisar.
