Amma, yawan masu jefa kuri'a ya kai 16 ne kawai, idan aka kwatanta da kashi 34 cikin 100 na zaben 2016 na baya, inda kashi 66 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a suka yi.
"Na zo ne don in yi zabe a madadin 'ya'yana da kuma inda muke a Turai", in ji Gjose Tanevski, mai shekara 62, wanda ya yi zabe a Skopje, babban birnin kasar.
A ranar 30 ga Satumba, 2018, a cikin kuri'ar da aka yi a Strumic a Makidoniya, Firayim Ministan Makidoniya Zoran Zaev, matarsa Zorica da ɗansa Dushko sun yi kuri'a game da sauya sunan Makidoniya.
