Paul Barreira, wani farfesa a Harvard Medical School kuma mataimakin shugaban jami'ar kiwon lafiya, ya ce jami'ar ta kammala koyar da darasi bayan ta ji yadda ɗalibai suke fama da rashin barci a lokacin mako guda na makaranta.
