Sarah Palin ta yi magana game da raunin da 'yarta ta ji a lokacin zaben Donald Trump
Ɗan Sarah Palin, Track Palin, mai shekara 26, ya yi shekara guda a Iraki bayan ya shiga rundunar soja a watan Satumba.
An kama Track Palin a daren Litinin da ya gabata, kuma an zarge shi da aikata mugunta a cikin iyali.
"Daga abin da ɗana na ke fuskanta a lokacin da ya dawo gida, zan iya kasancewa cikin iyalan da ke fuskantar sakamakon PTSD da kuma raunukan da sojoji na ƙasarmu da ke komawa gida suke sha", in ji ta a gaban taron da aka yi a Tulsa, Oklahoma, don bikin zaben Donald Trump.
