An kama Track Palin a birnin Wasilla, Alaska, a ranar Litinin, a cewar Dan Bennett, mai ba da rahoto ga 'yan sanda a Wasilla, an zarge shi da cin zarafin da ake yi wa mata a gida da kuma cin zarafin da ake yi wa mata a gida da kuma amfani da makamai a lokacin da ta sha giya.
Jihohi 18 da kuma yankin Columbia sun amince da sabon dokar 'yan gudun hijira
Jihohi 18 da kuma yankin Columbia sun nemi a canja sabon tsarin da ya shafi 'yan gudun hijira a Amurka, wanda ya ce ba za a ba da mafaka ga mutanen da ke gudun hijira daga tashin hankali ko kuma tashin hankali a gida ba.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da na tarayya sun ba da wasiƙar abokanan shari'a a Washington a ranar Juma'a, don tallafawa 'yan takarar mafaka da suka taka dokar, in ji NBC News.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai gabatar da kara ba a cikin shari'ar Grace vs. Sessions, wadda kungiyar 'yancin bil'adama ta Amurka ta yi a watan Agusta a kan manufofin tarayya.
Ta ce abokin tarayyarta da 'ya'yanta da ke cikin wata ƙungiya mai ƙarfi sun yi mata fyade.
An kama shi a Texas.
Babban mai gabatar da kara da ya goyi bayan Gracea ya kwatanta El Salvador da Honduras da kuma Guatemala, inda yawancin masu neman mafaka a Amurka suka fito, a matsayin ƙasashe inda gangami da tashin hankali a gida suke da matsala ga dukan fannoni na al'umma.
Sabon manufar 'yan gudun hijira ta Amurka ta soke hukuncin da hukumar da ke neman mafaka ta yanke a shekarar 2014 cewa baƙi marasa takaddama sun nemi mafaka saboda tashin hankali a cikin iyali.
A ranar Juma'a, Babban Lauyan Kotun Daular Columbia, Karl Racine, ya ce sabon layin ya yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na duniya.
Dokar tarayya ta bukaci a yanke hukunci a kan duk bukatar mafaka bisa ga gaskiyar da kuma yanayin da ake ciki, kuma irin wannan ƙuntatawa ya saɓa wa wannan ka'ida  kamar yadda aka faɗa a cikin wasiƙar 'Abokan Shari'a'.
Masu gabatar da kara sun kuma ce wannan dokar ta hana 'yan gudun hijira shiga Amurka tana cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka saboda masu zuwa za su iya zama 'yan kasuwa kuma su samu karin aiki.
A watan Yuni, Babban Shari'a Jeff Sessions ya umurci alƙalai da ke kula da harkokin shiga da su dakatar da ba da mafaka ga waɗanda suka tsere daga tashin hankali a gida da kuma gangami.
An yi amfani da mafaka don 'yan gudun hijira da ke gudun hijira daga ƙasarsu saboda zalunci ko tsoro na launin fata, addini, ƙasa ko wani ɓangare na zamantakewar al'umma ko ra'ayi na siyasa Sessions ya sanar da sabon tsarin mafaka a cikin jawabinsa na 11 ga watan Yuni.
Ba a taɓa yin amfani da mafaka don magance dukan matsalolin da mutane suke fuskanta a kowace rana a dukan duniya ba.
