"Halin yana da matukar damuwa", in ji Risa Kusuma, mai shekara 35, yayin da take kwantar da hankalinta daga zazzabin da take sha a wani cibiyar kwashe jariri a garin da ke cikin ruɓewar garin Palun.
A kowane minti, motar motar asibiti tana kawo sabbin gawawwakin mutane.
