Jakadan Amurka ya zargi kasar Sin da yin ta'addanci da kuma yada labaran da suka shafi cin hanci da rashawa
Wani jakadan kasar Sin na Amurka ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka a matsayin wata hanyar yada labaran, a mako guda bayan da wata jarida ta kasar Sin ta wallafa wani tallan shafi hudu a cikin jaridar Amurka da ke yaba wa yarjejeniyar cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China.
A ranar Laraba da ta gabata ne shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana game da wani shafi da aka biya na jaridar China Daily a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register, wadda ita ce jaridar da ta fi kowa karantawa a jihar Iowa, bayan da aka zargi kasar Sin da tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dattawa na 6 ga watan Nuwamba.
Sanarwar da Trump ya yi game da ƙoƙarin Beijing na tsoma baki a zaben Amurka, wani sabon mataki ne a yakin neman zaben Washington na matsa lamba a kan kasar Sin, jami'an Amurka da suka yi magana da Reuters.
Duk da cewa baƙon gwamnati na yau da kullum tana ba da sanarwar don inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a halin yanzu suna cikin rikice-rikicen kasuwanci mai yawa, inda bangarorin biyu ke ɗaukar nauyin haraji akan kayayyakin da suke fitarwa.
Masana a kasar Sin da Amurka sun ce a farkon yakin kasuwanci, an yi amfani da kudaden fansa na kasar Sin ne ga jihohin da suka goyi bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump kamar Iowa.
Terry Branstad, jakadan kasar Sin na Amurka kuma gwamnan jihar Iowa na dogon lokaci, ya ce Beijing ta yi wa ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni lahani.
A yanzu, da yake ƙara ƙalubalen da ake yi wa kasar Sin ta hanyar wallafa sanarwa ta yaɗa labarai a cikin jaridarmu ta 'yanci, Branstad ya rubuta a cikin wata sanarwa da ya buga a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi.
Ta wajen yada labaransa, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta amfana daga al'adun 'yancin magana da kuma jaridar da Amurka ta yi wa daraja ta hanyar saka wani sanarwa a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register, in ji Branstad.
A cikin jaridar Beijing, an ga bambancin ra'ayi a iyakacin lokaci, kuma ba a ga ainihin bambancin ra'ayi da 'yan kasar Sin za su iya samu game da ci gaban tattalin arzikin su ba.
Branstad ya ci gaba da cewa wata babbar jarida a kasar Sin ta ƙi buga labarin da ta rubuta, amma ba ta bayyana ainihin jaridar da take ba.
Kavanaugh ya yi watsi da 'yan majalisar Republican, masu bincike sun yi gargadin
Masu bincike sun ce cewa 'yan Republican da yawa da suka fi kowa suna goyon bayan Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi takarar a kotun koli, zai iya jawo musu wani mummunan sakamako musamman a zaben 'yan mata.
A halin yanzu, an yi ta yin tawaye da motsin zuciyar mutane game da wannan lamarin, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun bayyana cewa suna son su ci gaba da yin zabe.
"Ba za a iya kawar da irin waɗannan abubuwa ba", in ji Grant Reeher, wani farfesa a fannin ilimin gwamnati a Cibiyar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse, a cikin wata talifi da aka wallafa a jaridar The Hill a ranar Asabar.
Reeher bai yi imani da cewa sanatan Jeff Flake na 'yan Republican na Arizona na ƙarshe na FBI ba zai iya wartsake masu jefa kuri'a masu fushi.
'Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru a jiya ba, kuma ba za su manta da abin da ya faru a gobe ko a watan Nuwamba ba,' in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma mai ba da rahoto ga kungiyar 'yanci ta kasa ta MoveOn, a cewar jaridar da ta fito a birnin a ranar Juma'a.
A safiyar Juma'a, masu zanga-zangar sun rera waƙar "Maris na zuwa" a kan titunan majalisar dattijai yayin da 'yan Republican da ke mulkin majalisar shari'a suka yanke shawarar ci gaba da zaben Kavanaugh, duk da shaida da Dr. Christine Blasey Ford ta bayar, in ji Mic.
Ba za a iya tantance himma da kuma motsawar 'yan Democrat ba, in ji Stu Rothenberg, mai nazarin siyasa marar aiki a wata hira da shafin yanar gizon.
Mutane suna cewa, "An yi farin ciki sosai".
Amma zai iya zama mafi girma musamman ga mata masu jefa kuri'a da ba su da tabbaci a kusa da su da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a, masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29 da ba sa yawan kada kuri'a domin ba sa son shugaban kasa.
Masu bincike sun yi hasashen cewa za a yi wani abu idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da tabbatar da hakan tun kafin lokacin da Ford ya yi jawabi a gaban babban kotun da ya yi ikirarin cewa ya yi lalata da shi.
"Wannan yana kawo rikici ga jam'iyyar Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin jam'iyyar Republican ga tashar labarai ta NBC News a farkon makon da ya gabata.
Ba wai kawai batun kwamitin ne ko kuma na karshe ba, ko kuma ko za a yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi, amma yadda 'yan Republican suka yi aiki a kan batun da kuma yadda suka bi da Ford, Guy Cecil, shugaban ƙungiyar 'yan Democrat mai goyon bayan Priorities USA ya ce wa gidan talabijin.
Amma, Amirkawa sun nuna cewa sun rarrabu sosai a kan ko za su amince da shaidar Ford ko Kavanaugh idan yawancin mutane sun amince da wannan.
Wani sabon bincike da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na mutanen da suka amsa sun yi imani da shaidar Ford ko kuma sun yi imani da ita, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce sun yi imani da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce suna ganin cewa Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya a cikin shaidar da ya bayar, amma kashi 30 cikin ɗari ne suka ce hakan ne game da Ford.
Bayan da Flake ya ci gaba da bincike, FBI ta ci gaba da bincike kan zargin da Ford da kuma wata mai suna Deborah Ramirez suka yi, jaridar The Guardian ta ruwaito.
Ford ya shaida wa hukumar shari'a cewa Kavanaugh ya yi masa barazana a lokacin da yake da shekaru 17 a lokacin da yake shan giya.
Ramirez ya ce a lokacin da suke karatu a Yale a shekarun 1980, sai ya bayyana masa asalinsa a wani biki na dalibai.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo mai fadi yana shirin kaddamar da sabuwar hanyar sadarwa ta yanar gizo a kan Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ta duniya, ya kaddamar da wani shiri na farawa da zai yi gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Wani sabon shiri na masana'antar fasaha, Inrupt, wani kamfani ne wanda aka gina a kan dandamali na Solid na Berners-Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar yanke shawara a kan inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma wanda zai iya samun dama ga wani abu.
A wata hira da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi ba'a game da manufar Inrupt na "mulkin duniya".
"Ya kamata a yi yanzu", in ji shi, yana magana ne game da wani kamfani na farko.
Wannan shi ne lokaci na tarihi.
Wannan app yana amfani da fasahar Solid don mutane su iya ƙirƙirar bayanan sirri na kansu, wato POD.
Yana iya ɗauke da jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin abubuwan tunawa, kalandar, ɗakin karatu na kiɗa, da kuma wasu kayan aiki na mutum da na sana'a.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack, da Spotify, duk suna samuwa a cikin burauzar guda a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke da ban sha'awa game da bayanan sirri shi ne cewa yana dogara ne da mai amfani da abin da ya kamata ya samu.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "data-powered personal empowerment".
John Bruce, Shugaba na kamfanin, ya ce manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da albarkatu, matakai da kuma basira da ake bukata don kawo Solid ga kowa.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin yana da wani tsari na tsaro da Berners-Leen, Bruce, IBM suka saya, wasu masu haɓaka da aka yi hayar aiki tare da aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu ba da kyauta.
Masu bunkasa fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen su na musamman ta hanyar kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa tattaunawa da Facebook da Google game da ko za a iya samar wa mutane da cikakken canji inda za a juya duk tsarin kasuwancin su cikin dare ɗaya.
Ba mu tambayar su amincewa da wannan ba.
A cikin wata sanarwa da ya wallafa a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa aikin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu don daidaito da ingancin sabon cibiyar sadarwa na Solid.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya kawo sauyi a kan Intanet ta wajen kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Jami'ar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance babbar murya a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Berners-Lee ya ci gaba da kasancewa a matsayin mai kafa da kuma shugabanci na World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation, da Open Data Institute, bayan Inrupt ya fara aiki.
"Ina da tabbaci sosai game da zamanin da za a yi amfani da hanyar sadarwa", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: Birnin yana tunawa da wani jarumi na yakin duniya na farko
A shekara ta 100 bayan wannan, birnin yana bikin da firist kaɗai na cocin Ingila da ya yi aiki a matsayin soja da aka ba shi lambar yabo ta Victoria Cross.
An ba da lambar yabo ga Lt. Col. Bernard Vann a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, a sakamakon hare-haren da aka kai ƙauyukan Bellenglisen da Lehaucourt.
Amma bayan kwana huɗu, wani dan bindiga ya kashe Vann, ba tare da ya san cewa shi ne babban jami'in sojin Birtaniya ba.
Biyu daga cikin jikoki na Maryamu sun yi bikin baje kolin wani dutse a Rushden, Northamptonshire, a ranar Asabar da ta gabata.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Vann, ya ce abin da ya faru yana da "abin mamaki sosai", kuma an bayyana alamar shekaru 100 bayan mutuwar kakansa.
A ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Lt. Col. Vann ya jagoranci rundunarsa ta wuce Canal de Saint-Quentin a cikin hazo mai yawa da kuma wuta mai tsanani ta hanyar bindigogi da makamai.
Daga bisani, ya hau kan gaba kuma ya nuna ƙarfin hali sosai, ya jagoranci sojojin su ci gaba kafin ya fara yin amfani da shi don yin amfani da kansa a filin.
Lt. Col. Vann ya mutu ne a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918, wata guda kafin a kawo karshen yakin.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce aikin da kakansa ya yi shi ne abin da ba zan taɓa iya kwatanta shi ba, wani abu da zai sa a girmama shi.
Michael Vann Ya sauka tare da ɗan'uwansa Dr. James Vann a cikin wani biki bayan wani biki da Brentwood Imperial Youth Band ya yi.
Michael Vann ya ce yana da "girma" cewa za a yi masa ja-gora, kuma ya daɗa cewa: "Muna tuna da ɗaukakar wani jarumi na gaskiya".
