" Tom Daley ya ji kamar bai cancanta ba saboda jima'i "
Mai tsalle-tsalle mai suna Tom Daley, mai tsalle-tsalle a cikin ruwa kuma ɗan wasan Olympics, ya ce ya ji cewa ya fi kowa daraja domin ya kasance mai lalata, amma hakan ya motsa shi ya yi nasara.
Wani ɗan shekara 24 ya ce sa'ad da yake makarantar sakandare ne ya ga cewa ba kowa ba ne yake kama da ni.
Daley, wanda ya yi magana a kan shirin Desert Island Discs na gidan rediyo na Lauren Laverne, ya ce ya yi magana game da 'yancin gay don ya ba da bege ga wasu.
Ta kuma gaya mana cewa bayan haihuwar jariri, cin kofin Olympics bai da muhimmanci sosai.
Kristi Young, mai gabatar da shirin rediyo na dogon lokaci, ta yi hutu na watanni da yawa saboda rashin lafiya.
Da yake zama baƙo a shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya ce ya ji kamar ya fi kowa ƙanƙanta a lokacin da yake ƙarami, saboda ba a yarda da su a matsayin yara da kuma aiki.
Ta ce: "Har wa yau, waɗannan motsin rai, na ji kamar ba na kowa, sun zama gaskiya, kuma sun ba ni ƙarfin da nake bukata don in yi nasara.
Ta ce tana son ta nuna cewa ita ce "wani abu" don kada ta sa kowa baƙin ciki bayan an gano jima'i.
Wani dan wasan Olympics da ya yi nasara a gasar Olympics sau biyu ya zama babban mai ba da shawara ga 'yan LGBT, kuma yana yin zanga-zangar gasar Commonwealth a wannan shekara don yin kira ga aikata laifuka na luwaɗi a wasu ƙasashe.
Ta ce ta fito ne domin tana jin cewa tana da farin ciki da ta samu ta yi rayuwa a fili ba tare da wata matsala ba, kuma tana son ta ba da bege ga wasu mutane.
