Wani sabon jirgin yaki na Jamus ya sake jinkirta
A cewar kafofin yada labarai na yankin, sabon jirgin ruwan na rundunar sojan ruwa na Jamus da aka ƙaddara a shekarar 2014 ne zai maye gurbin kayan aikin da suka lalace a lokacin yakin sanyi, amma za a fara amfani da shi a farkon shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma tsadar da ake samu.
A cewar wani mai gabatar da rahoto ga jaridar Die Zeit, an dage aikin shigar da jirgin farko na sabon jirgin ruwa na Baden-Württemberg zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019.
An shirya cewa za a shiga cikin rundunar jiragen ruwa a shekara ta 2014, amma matsalolin da ke tattare da isar da kayayyaki sun hana wannan aikin mai ban sha'awa.
Ana ba da umarnin jiragen ruwa hudu na Baden-Württemberg da aka ba da umarni a cikin 2007 don maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Bayanai da aka samu sun nuna cewa suna da makamai masu ƙarfi, da tsarin kai-fuka don hana jiragen sama da jiragen sama, da kuma fasahar ɓoyewa, kamar su na yin amfani da na'urorin bincike da kuma rage ganuwa na siginar infrared da na sauti.
Abubuwan da ke cikin jirgin sun fi muhimmanci shi ne tsawon lokacin da ake kula da shi.
Amma, a cewar jaridar Die Zeit, ci gaba da jinkirta yana nufin cewa manyan sojojin da ake kira 'yan ta'adda'  da ake cewa suna da niyyar inganta tasirin Jamus a kasashen waje  sun riga sun tsufa a lokacin da suka shiga aikin.
A shekarar da ta shige, an yi sanarwa game da mummunan jirgin F125 da rundunar jiragen ruwa ta Jamus ta ƙi shigar da shi cikin jirgi kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa tashar jiragen ruwa ta Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar ta dawo da jirgin bayan an kai shi.
Ba a san dalilin da ya sa aka mayar da shi ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun yi magana game da muhimman abubuwan da ke cikin software da kayan aiki da ke sa jirgin ya zama abin da ba zai dace ba a aikin yaƙi.
Wannan rashin isasshen software yana da muhimmanci musamman domin jiragen ruwa na Baden-Württemberg suna da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa kimanin 120, wanda ya kai rabin ma'aikatan jiragen ruwa na Bremen-class.
Bugu da ƙari, an gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyi sosai, wanda ke rage aikinsa kuma yana iyakance damar da rundunar ke da ita don sabuntawa.
An ce jirgin Rhineland-Palatinate mai ƙarfin tan 7,000 ya ninka nauyin jirgin da Jamus ta yi amfani da shi a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Ban da rashin kayan aiki, akwai matsala a kan farashin dukan aikin.
An ce farashin ya karu zuwa na Euro 3.1 biliyan, daga na Euro 2.2 biliyan.
Matsalar samun sabbin jiragen ruwa ta taso ne bayan an yi gargadin cewa sojojin Jamus za su ragu.
A farkon wannan shekara, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus, Hans-Peter Bartels, ya ce jiragen ruwa da ke aiki a cikin rundunar jiragen ruwa na Jamus suna raguwa.
A cewar wani jami'in, matsalar ta kara muni a tsawon lokaci saboda an cire tsoffin jiragen ruwa daga aiki amma ba a maye gurbin su da sababbin ba.
Ya yi korafi cewa babu wani jirgin ruwa na Baden-Württemberg da aka yi amfani da shi a cikin rundunar jiragen ruwa.
