A ranar Lahadi, fadar White House ta sanar da cewa za a iya dage ganawar da Donald Trump ke yi da mataimakin ministan shari'a Rod Rosenstein a mako guda bayan da aka yi wani babban kotun da ke neman a yi masa shari'a a kan Brett Kavanaugh.
Rosenstein yana kula da aikin da Babban Sakataren Shari'a Robert Mueller ke yi, wanda ke bincika yadda Rasha ta shiga cikin zaben, da kuma yadda Trump ya yi amfani da mataimakansa wajen tuntuɓar Rasha da kuma yiwuwar shugaban ya yi amfani da shi wajen hana shari'a.
A Washington, an yi wata jita-jita cewa Trump zai kori mataimakin ministan shari'a, wanda zai sa mu yi rashin son kai a binciken Mueller.
A farkon wannan watan, New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya tattauna yiwuwar yin rikodin tattaunawar da Trump a ɓoye, da kuma yiwuwar kora shugaban kasa bisa ga Dokar Kwaskwarima ta 25.
