Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka afkawa garin Palun a Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, kuma jami'an sun ce adadin wadanda suka mutu na sa ran karuwa.
Saboda rashin sadarwa a yankin, hukumomin ceto ba su samu wani bayani daga yankin Donggala a arewacin Palun ba, wanda ya fi kusa da tsakiyar girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.5.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga cikin gobarar bayan da aka yi hatsarin.
Bayanai na musamman game da Palau da Donggala a Sulawes Island:
Palu ita ce babban birnin lardin Sulawes ta tsakiya, a bakin bakin teku mai zurfi a yammacin tsibirin Sulawes, kuma a shekarar 2017 an kiyasta yawan mutane 379,800.
A lokacin bikin cika shekaru 40 da birnin ya yi, girgizar ƙasa da tsunami sun auku.
Ƙasar Donggala tana da nisan mil 180 daga arewa maso yammacin Sulawesi.
A cikin shekara ta 2017, birnin Donggala yana da yawan jama'a 299,200.
Kasashen da ke yankin Sulawesi ta tsakiya, musamman yankin Donggala na bakin teku, suna da manyan harkokin tattalin arziki kamar su kifi da kuma noma.
Ana yin amfani da nickel don yin hakar ma'adinai, amma ana yin amfani da shi ne a bakin tekun Sulawesi, a Morowali.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, an yi tsunami da yawa a Palau da Donggala.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a birnin Donggala.
A shekara ta 1996, tsunami ya kai ga yammacin birnin Donggala kuma ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake kira Pacific Ring of Fire da ke fama da girgizar ƙasa.
Wasu daga cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami mafi tsanani a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a arewacin Sumatra, a yammacin tekun lardin Aceh, Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami a ranar 26 ga Disamba, wanda ya kai ga ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a tekun Tekun Indiya. Fiye da rabin waɗanda suka mutu sun kasance a yankin Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, an yi girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani a yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias a bakin tekun Sumatra.
A shekara ta 2006, girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afku a kudu da tsibirin Java, mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta jawo tsunami da ya kai kusan 700 a bakin tekun kudu na tsibirin.
A shekara ta 2009, girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Sumatra Mentawain, ta jawo tsunami mai tsayi na mita 10, wanda ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani girgizar ƙasa ta afkawa yankin Aceh Pidie Jaya, ta jawo lalacewa da firgici yayin da mutane ke tuna da babbar lalacewa da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004.
A wannan lokacin, babu tsunami, amma mutane fiye da 100 ne suka mutu sa'ad da gine-ginen suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok a Indonesia, ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasa ta halaka dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon buɗe ido a cikin keɓewa na ɗan lokaci.
