Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna tunanin yin hukuncin kisa ga wani mutum da ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York.
Masu gabatar da kara a jihar New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci da ya kashe mutane takwas a birnin New York, wanda ba a yi masa hukuncin kisa ba tun shekarar 1953 a jihar.
A cewar wannan shari'ar, Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot a watan Oktoba a lokacin da ya kai hari a kan titin babur na West Side Highway a kudancin Manhattan, inda ya yi amfani da ita wajen kai wa masu tafiya da kuma masu hawa keke.
Sanarwar da ke kan bukatar hukuncin kisa a yankin kudancin New York ta ce za a iya yin kisa idan masu gabatar da kara sun tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi musu mummunan rauni.
A cikin takardun shari'a, an ce za a iya yanke hukuncin kisa a kan waɗannan tuhuma biyu.
Bayan makonni bayan harin, kotu ta hukunta Saipov da laifin mutum 22, wanda ya hada da laifin kashe mutane takwas don taimakawa kungiyar ta'addanci. Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna amfani da wannan sunan a lokuta da suka shafi aikata laifuka da aka shirya.
Da yake an yi shiri sosai don kai hari, masu gabatar da kara sun bayyana yadda Saipov ya aikata abin da ya ɓata rai, da mugunta da kuma kunya.
Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadtin, Darren Drake, Ariel Erli, Hernan Ferruchin, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco illa da illa da kuma asararsu, in ji sanarwar da ta shafi tuhumar.
Daga cikin wadanda aka kashe, biyar daga cikinsu 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekara goma ta shige tun da kotun da ke kudancin New York ta yanke hukuncin kisa.
An samu wanda ake tuhuma da sunan Khalid Barnes da laifin kisan dillalan miyagun ƙwayoyi biyu, amma a ƙarshe an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai a watan Satumba na shekara ta 2009.
An yi amfani da hukuncin kisa a New York a shekarar 1953 a wani shari'ar tarayya, inda aka kashe Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata, a lokacin da suke yin yaƙi da Soviet Union shekaru biyu da suka shige, don yin ta'addanci.
An kashe su biyu a kan kujera a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cewar takardun shari'a, Saipov, wanda dan kasar Uzbekistan ne, bai nuna alamun tuba ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni da suka biyo bayan harin.
Ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa abin da ya yi yana da kyau, in ji 'yan sanda.
A cewar zargin, Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa ya samu wahayi zuwa harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa.
'Yan sanda sun ce Saipov ya so samun tikitin ISIS a cikin dakinsa na asibiti.
Ya amsa zargin da ake masa da cewa bai aikata laifi ba.
