Kungiyar Turai ta tabbatar da nasarar lashe gasar Ryder Cup a birnin Paris
Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018 ta hanyar doke ta Amurka ta 16,5 da 10,5 a filin Le Golf National a waje da Paris, Faransa.
