Ƙungiyar Turai ta riƙe kambin a kanta sa'ad da ta ci gaba da samun maki 14.5 da aka ba ta a dā, wato, ta hannun kyaftin din Denmark Thomas Bjørn.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson ya yi fama da matsaloli a kusan dukkanin gasar kuma ya buga wasan farko a cikin ruwa a kan 16 a kan layin par-3, yana ba da wasan ga Francesco Molinar.
